$-- %  VARIABLES -------------------------------------------------------------------
$-- % - $variable$                     -> Direct variable substitution
$-- % - $if(variable)$ ... $endif$     - > IF Conditional inclusion
$-- % - $if(variable)$ .$else$. $endif$ -> IF/ELSE Conditional inclusion
$-- % - $for(variable)$ ... $endfor$   -> Loop over list variables
